Group Results by Comparison

Source: R/helpers.R, R/margot_multi_arm_causal_forest.R
group_results_by_comparison.Rd

Groups the results of multi-arm causal forest analysis by comparison levels.

Groups custom evaluation tables by treatment comparison level.

Usage

group_results_by_comparison(results)

group_results_by_comparison(results)

Arguments

results

A list of model results.

results_list

A list of results from margot_multi_arm_causal_forest.

Value

A list of grouped results by comparison levels.

A list of data frames, one for each treatment comparison.
